Miscellaneous Highlights: This was the final game of the regular season series between the two teams
The Orioles swept the series with a 3-0 record
Others: The game was played at Target Field in Minneapolis, Minnesota
The game lasted 2 hours and 22 minutes
The umpires for the game were Todd Tichenor (home plate), Manny Gonzalez (first base), Cory Blaser (second base), and Nestor Ceja (third base)
